One question, how do you know it is a booby trap if you can't click on it?? It may sound terribly naive, but I'm looking to try and explain this to the rest of the staff and I'm not sure how to detect a real booby trap.  <br>
<br>
Are there any signs?? Any give aways?  Inquiring minds want to know how to tell the difference between a booby trap and a real link..<br>
<br>
In the mean time Mods, know you posters, and be aware of links posted in the posts of strangers... Anything questionable, email Yo and ask.. at least for now...<br>
<br>
And as soon as we learn how to detct a booby trap........<br>
<br>
Booby traps are edited out.. and the post removed to the Abyss.<br>
<br>
I'll begin a thread for booby traped posts...<br>
